<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="the-future">The future</h2>
<p>I want to explore the various quarters around Kuala Lumpur and what the city has to offer. My next port of call will probably be <a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/7nYdHKze1PXohFcy7">Malacca</a> and then further south towards Singapore, given that I now have a ticket!</p>
<p>Keep a look out for my next post.</p>


