<item>
  <title>Welcome</title>
  <dc:creator>Afsar Chowdhury</dc:creator>
  <link>https://afsarchowdhury.github.io/posts/2025-01-09-welcome/welcome.html</link>
  <description><![CDATA[ 





<p>If you are here, you are probably lost. Of all the places on the internet you could have gone to, and of all the things you could be doing with your life, you are here. You must be a rambler. Maybe not in person, but certainly in mind and in spirit.</p>
<div class="callout callout-style-default callout-note no-icon callout-titled">
<div class="callout-header d-flex align-content-center">
<div class="callout-icon-container">
<i class="callout-icon no-icon"></i>
</div>
<div class="callout-title-container flex-fill">
Ramble
</div>
</div>
<div class="callout-body-container callout-body">
<p>/răm′bəl/</p>
<p>An intransitive verb.</p>
<ul>
<li><p>To move about aimlessly. Synonym: wander.</p>
<blockquote class="blockquote">
<ul>
<li>“He roamed and rambled […] to the sparkling sands of her diamond deserts.”</li>
<li>The mind rambled for hours in the labyrinth of roads not taken.</li>
</ul>
</blockquote></li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
<p>Here, you will find my prosaic musings on some of my rambles.</p>



